'''赫姆辛人'''<ref name="观察者2011">{{cite web |title=苏联剧变中的民族因素 |url=https://www.guancha.cn/life/2011_08_15_59421.shtml |website=观察者网 |accessdate=2020-12-11 |date=2011-08-15}}</ref><ref name="敌人">{{cite web |title=谁是俄罗斯的“敌人” |url=http://news.163.com/special/00012Q9L/Russia100330.html |website=网易 |accessdate=2020-12-11 |archive-date=2020-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200113025942/http://news.163.com/special/00012Q9L/Russia100330.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-hy|Համշէնցիներ}}，{{lang|hy-latn|Hamshentsiner}}；{{lang-tr|Hemşinliler}}），也译为'''哈姆辛人'''、'''含姆辛人'''、'''哈姆申人'''等，[[亚美尼亚人|亚美尼亚人]]中的一个族群，也被视为由亚美尼亚人演化形成的独立民族，该族群得名于[[土耳其|土耳其]]东北部[[里泽省|里泽省]]的{{le|赫姆欣|Hemşin}}与{{le|恰姆勒赫姆欣|Çamlıhemşin}}地区<ref name="Bert Vaux pp.1-2">Vaux. ''Hemshinli'', pp. 1-2, 4-5.</ref><ref name="Peter Alford Andrews 1989. pp. 476-477">Peter Alford Andrews, ''Ethnic Groups in the Republic of Turkey''. Wiesbaden, Dr. Ludwig Reichert Verlag, 1989, pp. 476-477, 483-485, 491.</ref><ref>Simonian, Hovann H. "Hemshin from Islamicization to the End of the Nineteenth Century" in ''[http://hemshin.org/books/TheHemshin-Full.pdf The Hemshin: History, Society and Identity in the Highlands of Northeast Turkey] {{Wayback|url=http://hemshin.org/books/TheHemshin-Full.pdf |date=20130503043711 }}''. Hovann H. Simonian (ed.) London: Routledge, 2007, p. 80.</ref><ref>Hachikian, Hagop. "Notes on the Historical Geography and Present Territorial Distribution of the Hemshinli", in ''The Hemshin'', pp. 146-147.</ref>，在伊朗也有极少数分布。该族群原本与多数亚美尼亚人一样是信仰[[亚美尼亚使徒教会|亚美尼亚使徒教会]]的[[基督徒|基督徒]]，但在[[奥斯曼帝国|奥斯曼帝国]]时期转信成为[[逊尼派|逊尼派]][[穆斯林|穆斯林]]<ref>Simonian, Hovann H. "Preface" in ''The Hemshin: History, society and identity in the Highlands of Northeast Turkey''. Hovann H. Simonian (ed.) London: Routledge, 2007, p. xx.</ref>，在伊朗则为什叶派。

